params.beacon: the beacon address to be added/tracked
params.beaconAlias: the beacon address to be added/tracked

params.collection: the collection for which to get the pointed beacon

returns._0: the beacon address pointed by the collection

params.beaconAlias: the beacon alias to be attributed to the newly deployed beacon
params.implementation: the beacon address to be added/tracked
